 ('1', '12', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Orangina refreshed their brand identity Achtung!/Kraftwerk wastasked to extend their newbrand identity to a fresh online experience. ', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'medium', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, '2016-02-26 10:46:08', '2016-03-31 13:17:23', '9d09384c-6dde-46b8-bc11-280ecfd90561'),
 ('2', '14', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'medium', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-26 11:34:33', '2016-03-31 13:17:23', '9a32a5d3-040e-4261-9dce-f7f7cb9ddcaf'),
 ('3', '17', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Strategy, Concept & UX', 'The content of the new Orangina website was meant to be kept simple serving a few main purposes.', 'In general there were two main obectives, informing people about the available range of Orangina products and telling them about the history of Orangina as a brand. The homepage would then serve as a hub to these two objectives, as well as to the Orangina social channels.', '#fdaa31', NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, '2016-02-26 13:29:08', '2016-03-31 13:17:23', 'fbd00b0a-afbb-480c-8dfc-2af114fa5dbd'),
 ('4', '19', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#fdaa31', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'medium', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '156418367', '2016-02-26 13:53:26', '2016-03-31 13:17:23', '5f04cbfa-691a-4dbf-938d-2cec2d65d4c1'),
 ('5', '20', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Design elements', 'Colors for the Orangina website were besides the brands Blue and Yellow, based on the labels of the different flavours. ', '', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'medium', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, '2016-02-26 14:02:48', '2016-03-31 13:17:23', '940efd6c-e536-4690-805e-78e47b133327'),
 ('6', '22', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-26 14:08:10', '2016-03-31 13:17:23', '4ac5c5e9-72e5-405e-8e59-9c8d996b6af0'),
 ('7', '23', 'en_us', 'Iconography', 'To add on the playfull, quirky identity of Orangina, we created an iconset that was used throughout the website.', 'Our hands on mentality can be found throughout the whole process. We bring ideas to life early. We prototype to keep improving along the way. ', '#ffffff', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'small', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-26 14:13:03', '2016-03-31 13:17:23', '00cc44c8-71e5-44dd-9b76-ec8970af2308'),
 ('8', '25', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Final Designs', 'The content of the new Orangina website was meantto be kept simple serving a few main purposes.', 'In general there were two main obectives, informing people about the available range of Orangina products and telling them about the history of Orangina as a brand. The homepage would then serve as a hub to these two objectives, as well as to the Orangina social channels.', '#092865', NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'medium', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, '2016-02-29 09:37:51', '2016-03-31 13:17:23', 'a9daad8f-5572-4053-a90f-701e74df278f'),
 ('9', '29', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#092865', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'small', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-29 09:41:30', '2016-03-31 13:17:23', '51d70b8e-83e4-424e-920a-2cd4be855f5f'),
 ('12', '80', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A website that lets fans share their love for Chocomel, seamlessly integrated with a delicious product showcase.', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'big', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, '2016-03-16 15:28:59', '2016-03-29 13:10:55', 'faf260b0-95a5-4a62-b47b-ee0ea1107b56'),
 ('13', '81', 'en_us', 'Designing for a love brand', 'When we were asked to design the brand portal for Chocomel we knew it was about chocolate love. A lot of loyal fans have a healthy obsession for this tasty chocolate drink.', 'Chocomel wanted to position themselves as an A-brand bevarage along with the common soft drinks. Their previous image was more cozy and soft. The new image on the otherhand was to be more fashionable and exclusive.', '#391f12', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, 'big', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 15:28:59', '2016-03-29 13:10:55', 'fbb4c01a-dce6-40c8-b03b-2605d901d98b'),
 ('14', '83', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'big', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 15:33:25', '2016-03-29 13:10:55', '17b736ea-105e-4688-8b83-09574c1cad2e'),
 ('15', '86', 'en_us', 'The voice of chocomel lovers', 'Instead of Chocomel telling visitors how great Chocomel really is, we engaged the already big group of fans and let them speak for the brand.', 'In a mix of owned and shared content, the homepage is build up from quotes on twitter, fanphotos on instagram and videos on youtube.', '#f0e9e4', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#391f10', NULL, NULL, 'none', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 15:46:55', '2016-03-29 13:10:55', '4502ba85-9b22-45c4-873e-a0ff7907b663'),
 ('16', '89', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Enjoying your Chocomel hot or cold?', 'Winter or summer, Chocomel can be consumed\r\nboth hot and cold. ', 'Depending on the season, we present the hero product in a warm mug or a cold glass. Since there is an ever lasting discussion on how Chocomel should be consumed, we gave users the option to switch.', '#391f12', NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'big', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 15:54:54', '2016-03-29 13:10:55', '58ceab7e-d5da-4da7-8ca7-b5a17ee6751f'),
 ('17', '90', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 15:54:54', '2016-03-29 13:10:55', 'f8fe58f2-8383-49b3-b935-c6c7731c7c39'),
 ('18', '91', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Life sized photography', 'When it comes to the product, we let the iconic photography speak.', 'In a colorful design, we showed visitors life size photography of the iconic Chocomel pack paired with a hot mug or a cool glass. The product pages has all the key information visitors want to know about their drink: nutritional information, ingredints, pack sizes and tell about the durable chocolate that is used in the drink.', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'small', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 16:47:03', '2016-03-29 13:10:55', 'c91180b6-0f74-4e9b-a673-126bc061460b'),
 ('19', '93', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'small', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 16:53:30', '2016-03-29 13:10:55', '33b6f29c-8974-4040-938c-b2ca0c2160ed'),
 ('20', '101', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A site that looks sharp  accross every screen', 'The grid view helps when scaling the website, by defining the number of horizontal columns the site looks great across all devices and screens. ', 'Massive screens gets a 5 column grid while small screens like phone get a modified 2 columns grid. ', '#f0e9e4', NULL, NULL, '#3b1f10', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'big', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, '2016-03-17 00:25:22', '2016-03-29 13:10:55', '27ac5317-3fa1-4599-873a-b444f9cd836b'),
 ('21', '102', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#f0e9e4', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'small', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-17 00:25:22', '2016-03-29 13:10:55', 'e3543a97-5ddb-4c54-ab6f-7f1cf1377caf'),
 ('22', '111', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-18 14:22:49', '2016-03-30 15:34:30', '28b9cd97-630e-4ad6-aa62-9ac121b0fbbd'),
 ('23', '130', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Layover with a Local offers KLM travelers with a stop of 6 hours or more at Amsterdam Schiphol Airport the opportunity to turn this transfer into a trip. ', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'big', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, '2016-03-18 14:33:19', '2016-03-29 13:14:11', 'daa8b390-1446-481f-a0c7-1dd706f649f2'),
 ('24', '132', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '123456', '2016-03-18 14:35:21', '2016-03-29 13:14:11', 'ea129ca9-3689-46fc-b134-28c8b7495305'),
 ('25', '134', 'en_us', '70% of travelers have a layover in Amsterdam', 'With Amsterdam Central Station just 15 minutes away, why not make use of it? Adventure is just around the corner. ', 'By connecting travelers to locals we turn waiting time into wander time, and for KLM its just another way to take you somewhere.', '#ffffff', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'big', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-18 14:38:01', '2016-03-29 13:14:12', '6e8cd117-1d20-4667-8cf2-c8570378cac2'),
 ('26', '136', 'en_us', 'Intelligent matchmaking based on interests', 'The element of matching up passengers with locals through a social profile can give hesitation. ', 'Therefore, the app uses intelligent matchmaking based on interests, shared languages and availability. Once the traveler requests a meetup, we select 3 locals and notify them with a push notification. ', '#ffffff', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'big', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-18 14:49:53', '2016-03-29 13:14:12', 'd6452946-f960-4d3b-b439-417609ae0b77'),
 ('27', '137', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A personal layover guide for travelers', 'Leaving the airport during a layover is potentially stressful. Thats why we created a personal layover guide that gives the traveler step-by-step directions.', 'The layover guide is made up from dynamic cards that offer relevant actions at the appropiate times. Real-time notifications ensure that the traveler returns to the airport in time.', '#00a1de', NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'big', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, '2016-03-18 14:53:28', '2016-03-29 13:14:12', '764c63fe-f13c-45da-aa90-2824fc7e2fc7'),
 ('29', '141', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#00a1de', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-18 14:57:27', '2016-03-29 13:14:12', '186b5405-70c3-473c-aeb4-161beac9390e'),
 ('30', '143', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'big', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '123456', '2016-03-18 15:33:27', '2016-03-29 13:14:12', '333872e1-d30d-4ada-b67b-be9daabbb934'),
 ('31', '145', 'en_us', 'An all-inclusive mini trip', 'In collaboration with the national railway company we offer the traveler a free train ticket into the city.', 'But there is more. At selected bars, they can get their first drink for free, available through an in-app coupon. As a local, you can set your availability so you can meet up with travelers only when you really want to.', '#ffffff', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'small', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-18 15:34:41', '2016-03-29 13:14:12', 'a8589534-a0f3-4492-9882-f622956b4a5a'),
 ('32', '147', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'So, how do we get the locals to sign up?', 'Were targeting locals that have an intrinsic motivation to meet up. Language students, for example, can practice their italian with a real italian. ', 'In collaboration with language schools, the expat centre and local bars we make sure to find locals that are excited for a meetup. One lucky local will win a ticket to the country of the traveler.', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'big', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, '2016-03-18 15:44:32', '2016-03-29 13:14:12', '8e6d0e1d-16bd-47e5-8e99-f5b52193e000'),
